Package: OrdPower
Type: Package
Title: OrdPower
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Sijing Shao, Ziqian Xu, Ross Jacobucci
Maintainer: Sijing Shao <sshao2@nd.edu>
Description: This package provides the pipelines for power analysis of longitudinal models with ordinal outcome variables using a simulation-based approach. Users can specify different sample sizes, timepoints, skewness of effects etc. when performing power analysis.
